text: Kevin Downes (born September 21, 1972) is an American film actor, writer, producer and director. Downes grew up in Visalia, California, three hours north of Los Angeles. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from California Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American television producers Category:Movie directors from California Category:Movie producers from California Category:Screenwriters from California
